data.description: Nestled in the Heart of New London with a large fenced in back yard. This move-in ready Home offers 3 Bedrooms and 1 Full Bath. Beautiful wood burning fireplace and hardwood floors throughout the first floor. Located just minutes from Downtown New London, L&M, Ocean Beach and all of New London's favorite local spots. Perfect rental investment opportunity as well with low taxes and maintenance. Schedule your showing today.
